               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18150405-84-cd455" type="crimeDate">30th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150405-84-off454 t18150405-84-cd455"></join>, a shawl, value 2 s. and a cloak, value 3 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18150405-84-victim792" type="victimName">
                        Sophia 
                        Newman
                     <interp inst="t18150405-84-victim792" type="surname" value="Newman"></interp>
