            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150405-84-person793">
                  SOPHIA 
                  NEWMAN
               <interp inst="t18150405-84-person793" type="surname" value="NEWMAN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150405-84-person793" type="given" value="SOPHIA"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150405-84-person793" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 30th of March, I was coming from the public-house with a pint of beer, a sailor followed me, and took my cloak and my shawl off my shoulders; I turned my head round, and saw it was the prisoner; he ran away; I called stop thief; he was stopped, and taken to the watchhouse. I am sure he is the man.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181504050046"></xptr>
            
                  <persName id="t18150405-84-person794">
                  SAMUEL 
                  TEDDY
               <interp inst="t18150405-84-person794" type="surname" value="TEDDY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150405-84-person794" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150405-84-person794" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the watchman that stopped the prisoner, upon the cry of stop thief; he said, it was his own mother that cried stop thief; I stopped him until the prosecutrix came up, and then I took him to the watchhouse; he was searched; nothing was found upon him.</p>
               <p>GUILTY aged 27.</p>
               <p>
